00:26:43,270 --> 00:26:44,270
Apa?

403
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:48,400
Aku ingin melakukannya sendiri.

404
00:26:50,610 --> 00:26:51,740
Satu hal kalau hanya melihat.

405
00:26:51,770 --> 00:26:53,210
Hal lain jika sebenarnya melakukan.

406
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:55,140
Aku tahu.
