443
00:28:36,780 --> 00:28:38,510
Baiklah.

444
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:40,510
Terima kasih.

445
00:28:46,190 --> 00:28:48,820
"Jika Cole menghubungimu, beritahu kami"?

446
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:50,560
